comments: Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in Conley's (MIN) path and marginal upper body contact occurs as the pick is set.
Finney-Smith (BKN) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) does not maintain verticality and initiates contact with Thomas's (BKN) arm that affects his post shot attempt.
Conley (MIN) establishes himself in Finney-Smith's (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Claxton (BKN) brings his hands toward Conley (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Claxton releases away to roll.
Gobert (MIN) places his hand on the back of Claxton's (BKN) left arm as he cuts through the lane and the contact is marginal.
Gobert (MIN) and Bridges (BKN) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Gobert (MIN) deflects the ball out of bounds.
Edwards (MIN) is moving alongside Bridges' (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Conley (MIN) deflects the pass out of bounds.
McDaniels (MIN) is drawn forwards into Bridges (BKN) and he initiates body contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Bridges (BKN) crosses the plane of the free throw line before his free throw attempt makes contact with the rim.
Dinwiddie (BKN) reaches towards Edwards (MIN) but fails to make contact with him.
